{"tid":1080224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國有金執，捐屎每次有500人仔？","createTime":"2019-03-27T12:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T12:54:45.000Z","uid":50534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39b8e2f6d14ca7bf96321f15c289bf4f6d09e95d","tid":1080224,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/03/27/donate-shit-each-time-there-is-a-return-of-rmb-500/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F03%2F27%2Fdonate-shit-each-time-there-is-a-return-of-rmb-500%2F&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=cf38555f\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/03/27/donate-shit-each-time-there-is-a-return-of-rmb-500/</a><br />\n據報導，近日廣州多所醫院接受「捐屎」，每次最高可獲五百元人民幣補償，網友就表示：「我能捐到你破產」。原來，大便在醫院能物盡其用也有不一樣的價值。<br />\n<br />\n拿著糞便去捐，相信都是很難接受的，不過糞便在醫學上也大有用處，所以有償捐獻也就不驚訝了。 糞便經特殊處理，可由膠囊口服或懸移液移植入患者腸道內，原理是拿正常人腸道中細菌來替換掉患者腸道裡失衡的菌群。醫生表示，目前糞菌移植主要用戶臨床研究，目前已經有幾千例了。<br />\n<br />\n此外，目前像心臟病、糖尿病、自閉症、抑鬱症等疾病都在嘗試糞菌移植，非常看好前景，移植成功還能幫助病人恢復健康。<br />\n<br />\n其實，這已經不是第一次募捐糞便，最早的捐獻能追溯到 2015 年，不過醫院用於治療的糞便常常是不公開募捐的，所以能拿到最高五百元的補償也不是人人皆可。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/EBABE2F7-A6A5-4686-9BC2-6A9F65A316BA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FEBABE2F7-A6A5-4686-9BC2-6A9F65A316BA.jpg&h=dbce881a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/76677788.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F76677788.jpg&h=8b128cf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"935e6de24f879abc4650fc8319231543480e0dca","tid":1080224,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f29c1ee1c028ea3d0b6802e529575cf8c5d340","tid":1080224,"uid":45165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"等睇連登仔頂爛市"},{"pid":"9f30b3646dadfc0a46546aa47281245148621657","tid":1080224,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:49:54.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩玩屎.jgp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1668d307508728af26571810583ea5f32630c206","tid":1080224,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"假新聞下嘩<br />\n<br />\n一係強國人弱智<br />\n<br />\nGI disease 補返d 共生菌都講得通<br />\n<br />\n屌你 CNS 都可以食屎醫？<br />\n<br />\n弱智連登仔先信"},{"pid":"1c415d4415701edc2556d118f59601c313417b88","tid":1080224,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"食屎醫自閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcbbfc9a53bc64c362c453ca70b136a415a90be","tid":1080224,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1668d307508728af26571810583ea5f32630c206","tid":1080224,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"假新聞下嘩<br />\n<br />\n一係強國人弱智<br />\n<br />\nGI disease 補返d 共生菌都講得通<br />\n<br />\n屌你 CNS 都可以食屎醫？<br />\n<br />\n弱智連登仔先信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"支那種不嬲弱智"},{"pid":"3b56e90b12f2305c7b11ff803616fc6a019e9faa","tid":1080224,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"香港都有捐屎, 不過搵唔到了"}]}